additional_info:
If you wish to have another language to choose from, you need to add the following lines to the css:
<pre>
.interwiki-[[lan]]{
    display:block!important;
}
</pre>
[[lan]] is a two-character abbreviation for the language you want to use, e.g. "en" for English, "de" for German, "fr" for French and so on. If you can't figure out the right one, you might want to have a look at the sourcecode of your favourite article on wikipedia (make sure it actually exists in you language...) and search for your language.


Versions:

1.1  -  Works for Chrome too. Bugfixes.
1.0  -  Initial release.

css:
@namespace url(http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml);

@-moz-document domain("wikipedia.org") {

@media screen and (max-width: 930px) {
    #mw-panel{
        display:none;
    }
    #right-navigation{
        margin-right:0%!important;
    }

    #left-navigation{
        margin-left:0%!important;
    }
}

#mw-page-base{
    opacity: 0;
}

#mw-panel{
    max-width:10px;
    opacity:0;
    position:fixed!important;
    margin-left:-15px;
}

#mw-panel:hover{
    max-width:200px;
    opacity:1;
}

#p-lang.portal.expanded ul{
    overflow:auto;
    max-height:500px;
    min-width:150px!important;
    width:100%!important;
}

#p-lang.portal ul{
    overflow:auto;
    max-height:500px;
    min-width:150px!important;
    width:100%!important;
}

pre {
    max-width:100%;
    white-space: pre-wrap;
}


#p-lang li{
    margin-top:-3px!important;
}

.wbc-editpage{
    position: absolute;
    left: 28px;
}

#p-lang.portal ul li{
    display:none;
}

.interwiki-en{
    display:block!important;
}

.interwiki-de{
    display:block!important;
}

.interwiki-fr{
    display:block!important;
}

.interwiki-es{
    display:block!important;
}

.portal{
    padding-bottom:0!important;
}

#content.mw-body{
    margin: 0 auto!important;
    width: 62%;
    box-shadow: 0 0 7px #ccc;
    border-style:none!important;
    min-width: 600px;
    max-width: 1100px;
    margin-top:-20px!important;
    font-size:1.1em!important;
    hyphens:auto;
    text-align:justify;
}
#content.mw-body h3{
    text-align:left;
}
#content.mw-body h2{
    text-align:left;
}

#firstHeading.firstHeading{
    text-align:center;
    font-size:2em!important;
    padding-bottom:5px!important;
}

#footer{
    margin: 0 auto!important;
    width: 62%;
    border-style:none!important;
    min-width: 600px;
    max-width: 1000px;

}

#mw-head{
    margin: 0 auto!important;
    min-width: 300px;
    position:fixed!important;
    right:auto!important;
    left:auto!important;
    top:-10px!important;
    opacity:0!important;
    background-color:#fff;
    border-bottom-style:solid;
    border-width:1px;
    border-color:#dddded;
}
#mw-head:hover{
    opacity:1!important;
}
#p-personal{
    visibility:hidden;
    height:0;
    display:none;
}

#p-search{
    margin-top:3px;
}

#right-navigation{
    margin-right:14%;
    position:static;
    margin-top:0!important;
    margin-left:5px;
}

#left-navigation{
    margin-top:0!important;
    position:static;
    top:auto!important;
    left:auto!important;
    margin-left:14%;
    margin-right:5px;
}

#left-navigation:hover{
    opacity:1;
    height:auto!important;
}

.mw-editsection{
    color:#ddd!important;
}
.mw-editsection a{
    color:#ddd!important;
}
}
